</p>
<p>Make sure this has the <code>AppBundle</code> namespace. We're going to fill this with functions
that work with Stripe, like <code>createCustomer()</code> or <code>updateCustomerCard()</code>.</p>
<h2 id="moving-createcustomer">Moving createCustomer() <a class="headerlink" href="centralize-stripe-code#moving-createcustomer" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>In the controller, the first thing we do is create a Customer:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="57faf7bb91">
