<p>Now the <code>StripeClient</code> class is getting dangerous!</p>
<h2 id="always-setting-the-api-key">Always setting the API Key <a class="headerlink" href="centralize-stripe-code#always-setting-the-api-key" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
