</p>
<p>Phew! This was a giant step sideways - but not only is our code more re-usable, it
just makes a lot more sense when you read it!</p>
<p>Double-check to make sure it works. Add something to your cart. Check-out. Yes!
No error! The system still works and this <code>StripeClient</code> is really, really sweet.</p>

    
